column3: “I’m located in Sumter SC. Luckily I’m able to access this strain. You looking for something to turn a few heads then look no further than “Super Glu”. How the young folk say it, “Big ⛽️“.”

“Very strong in smell, loud enough to wake a surrounding neighbor. Definitely great for appetite and relaxing. Buds are more fluffy than sticky but still as a consistent sticky touch throughout a finger tip breakdown.”
